#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:2
#: eb004d6df9a0452c9595de807dc35cf3
msgid "Cantilever Beam"
msgstr "悬臂梁"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:4
#: 5dea76ba32f44fd4a2cbfac34018844c
msgid ""
"The textbook entry-point for solid mechanics in TensorMesh: a :math:`2.0 "
"\\times 0.2 \\times 0.2` m steel cantilever clamped at one end, loaded by a "
"downward force at the other. Linear small-strain elasticity, one direct "
"linear solve, ~30 lines of code. The script is "
"``examples/solid/cantilever_beam/cantilever_beam.py``."
msgstr ""
"TensorMesh 中固体力学的教科书式入门示例：一根 :math:`2.0 \\times 0.2 \\times 0.2` m "
"的钢制悬臂梁，一端固定，另一端施加向下的力。线性小应变弹性，一次直接线性求解，约 30 行代码。脚本位于 "
"``examples/solid/cantilever_beam/cantilever_beam.py``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:13
#: d50f87f3d277435a924c4f48838f1e71
msgid "Problem"
msgstr "问题"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:15
#: e9af9df3b74d4f7fa1be8d3a228af3a4
msgid "Small-strain linear elasticity:"
msgstr "小应变线弹性："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:17
#: 13132bb4c6214cf69dd2177edf4a616f
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\nabla \\cdot \\boldsymbol{\\sigma} \\;=\\; \\mathbf{0}\n"
"\\quad \\text{in } \\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\boldsymbol{\\sigma} \\;=\\; \\mathbb{C} : \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon} = \\tfrac12 (\\nabla\\mathbf{u} + \\nabla\\mathbf{u}^T),"
msgstr ""
"\\nabla \\cdot \\boldsymbol{\\sigma} \\;=\\; \\mathbf{0}\n"
"\\quad \\text{in } \\Omega,\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\boldsymbol{\\sigma} \\;=\\; \\mathbb{C} : \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon} = \\tfrac12 (\\nabla\\mathbf{u} + \\nabla\\mathbf{u}^T),"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:26
#: 90ad7e9176414c6eb095413f508e3836
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"where :math:`\\mathbb{C}` is the isotropic stiffness tensor with Young's "
"modulus :math:`E = 200` GPa and Poisson's ratio :math:`\\nu = 0.3`. Boundary"
" conditions:"
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`\\mathbb{C}` 是各向同性刚度张量，杨氏模量 :math:`E = 200` GPa，泊松比 :math:`\\nu = "
"0.3`\\ 。边界条件："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:30
#: e6cdf01899804c39a874fa6d042830da
#, python-brace-format
msgid "clamp at :math:`x = 0`: :math:`\\mathbf{u} = \\mathbf{0}`,"
msgstr "在 :math:`x = 0` 处固定：\\ :math:`\\mathbf{u} = \\mathbf{0}`\\ ，"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:31
#: ae9b74f690b14c3583be44edc7882a05
msgid ""
"tip load at :math:`x = 2`: total force :math:`F = -100` kN distributed over "
"the right face nodes,"
msgstr "在 :math:`x = 2` 处的端部载荷：总力 :math:`F = -100` kN，分布于右端面节点上，"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:33
#: 97e6cd91b9a7468397344b827385cdcc
msgid "all other surfaces: traction-free."
msgstr "其余所有表面：无面力（自由）。"

