#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:82
#: 71daa8011d23434da2ea30a16161f9c5
msgid "A few details that make this short:"
msgstr "几个让代码如此简短的细节："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:84
#: 8b0a50c43d964bce850f575d619ccb55
msgid ""
":class:`~tensormesh.LinearElasticityElementAssembler` is a built-in vector-"
"valued assembler — it returns a stiffness block of size ``[mesh.dim, "
"mesh.dim]`` per (test, trial) basis pair, all wrapped into one "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix` of shape ``[mesh.dim * n_points, "
"mesh.dim * n_points]``. See :doc:`../../user_guide/forms` for the "
"convention."
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.LinearElasticityElementAssembler` "
"是一个内置的向量值装配器——它为每一对（测试、试探）基函数返回一个大小为 ``[mesh.dim, mesh.dim]`` "
"的刚度块，并将它们全部封装进一个形状为 ``[mesh.dim * n_points, mesh.dim * n_points]`` 的 "
":class:`~tensormesh.sparse.SparseMatrix`\\ 。约定参见 "
":doc:`../../user_guide/forms`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:90
#: b05bc897f1284c0e8a929c9185192dd3
msgid ""
"The DOF layout is per-node ``[u_x, u_y, u_z]``; "
"``torch.repeat_interleave(fixed_node_mask, dim)`` lifts the per-node mask to"
" per-DOF."
msgstr ""
"自由度按节点排布为 ``[u_x, u_y, u_z]``\\ ；\\ "
"``torch.repeat_interleave(fixed_node_mask, dim)`` 把逐节点的掩码提升为逐自由度的掩码。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:93
#: 4ef6fb0708104839ac01c0d3f12af307
msgid ""
":mod:`tensormesh.material` ships predefined isotropic materials (``Steel``, "
"``Aluminum``, ``Rubber``, ``Bone``) so you don't have to memorize :math:`E` "
"and :math:`\\nu`."
msgstr ""
":mod:`tensormesh.material` 提供了预定义的各向同性材料（\\ ``Steel``\\ 、\\ ``Aluminum``\\ "
"、\\ ``Rubber``\\ 、\\ ``Bone``\\ ），这样你就无需记忆 :math:`E` 和 :math:`\\nu`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:96
#: 90af2e27b5e74c489f6edcb6a4a1da5d
msgid ""
"``plot_deformation`` exaggerates the deformation by ``scale=50`` for "
"visibility — the actual tip displacement is on the order of millimeters."
msgstr "``plot_deformation`` 通过 ``scale=50`` 放大变形以便观察——实际的端部位移仅为毫米量级。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:102
#: de8bda37014046f480bd473daa7b248f
msgid "Sanity check"
msgstr "合理性检验"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:104
#: 75af0506753c4af6a6ba0f7002ea4eb1
msgid ""
"For a tip-loaded prismatic cantilever, Euler-Bernoulli beam theory predicts "
"a tip deflection"
msgstr "对于端部受载的等截面悬臂梁，欧拉-伯努利梁理论预测的端部挠度为"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:107
#: 1fbd1fda9bc049369ffc838c47998b13
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\delta \\;=\\; \\frac{F\\, L^3}{3\\, E\\, I},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"I = \\frac{b\\, h^3}{12},"
msgstr ""
"\\delta \\;=\\; \\frac{F\\, L^3}{3\\, E\\, I},\n"
"\\qquad\n"
"I = \\frac{b\\, h^3}{12},"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:113
#: 752774fe5ed24f00a361ed0ec3fd2b27
msgid ""
"with :math:`L = 2` m, :math:`b = h = 0.2` m, :math:`E = 200` GPa, :math:`F ="
" 10^5` N. That gives :math:`\\delta \\approx 5.0` mm. The FEM solution at "
"the right-face center should agree to within the coarse-mesh approximation "
"error (a few percent at ``chara_length=0.08``)."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`L = 2` m，\\ :math:`b = h = 0.2` m，\\ :math:`E = 200` GPa，\\ "
":math:`F = 10^5` N。由此得到 :math:`\\delta \\approx 5.0` "
"mm。有限元解在右端面中心处的结果应与之吻合，误差不超过粗网格的近似误差（在 ``chara_length=0.08`` 时为百分之几）。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:119
#: 885a6945ab3746d68ffefc869772edc7
msgid ""
"Steel cantilever beam — deformed shape with tip load, displacement coloring"
msgstr "钢制悬臂梁——端部受载下的变形形状，按位移着色"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/cantilever_beam.rst:123
#: b5b7c2891fc949cca52c106219b54629
msgid ""
"Output of ``cantilever_beam.py``. The undeformed beam is drawn in light "
"grey; the deformed configuration is colored by displacement magnitude. Blue "
"cubes mark fixed nodes at :math:`x=0`; red arrows mark the distributed tip "
"load on the :math:`x=L` face. The deformation is exaggerated by ~62× so the "
"bending is visible at this aspect ratio — the actual tip displacement is on "
"the order of millimeters and matches the Euler-Bernoulli closed form to "
"within the coarse-mesh approximation error."
msgstr ""
"``cantilever_beam.py`` 的输出。未变形的梁以浅灰色绘制；变形后的构型按位移大小着色。蓝色立方体标记 :math:`x=0` "
"处的固定节点；红色箭头标记 :math:`x=L` 面上分布的端部载荷。变形被放大了约 62 "
"倍，以便在此长宽比下能看清弯曲——实际的端部位移仅为毫米量级，与欧拉-伯努利闭式解吻合，误差不超过粗网格的近似误差。"

